<p>TBC Provide a "warning" template, with a nice-looking icon and appropriate framing (light red fieldset, for example). Investigate Tango icons. Needs some CSS tweaking.</p>

<h3><a name="index2h3"></a>Notes</h3>

<p>TBC Provide a "note" template, similar to the "warning" one (yellow-greyish maybe).</p>

